## 2. ML Models (downloaded at runtime)

These models are **not** shipped with whicc. They are downloaded from HuggingFace
on first run by `src/model_manager.py` into `~/Library/Application Support/whicc/models/`.
Each model is governed by its own license; whicc makes no modifications to the
weights.

| Model | HuggingFace ID | Source | License | Role |
|---|---|---|---|---|
| Qwen3-ASR-0.6B-4bit | `mlx-community/Qwen3-ASR-0.6B-4bit` | Alibaba (Qwen3) → MLX community port | Apache 2.0 (Qwen3 base) | Chinese ASR |
| Nemotron 3.5 ASR Streaming 0.6B | `mlx-community/nemotron-3.5-asr-streaming-0.6b` | NVIDIA → MLX community port | NVIDIA Open Model License | English ASR |
| Hy-MT2-1.8B-GGUF / Hy-MT2-7B-GGUF | (loaded by user in LM Studio / vLLM) | Tencent | Tencent Model License (research/commercial OK) | Translation |

Users are responsible for reviewing and complying with each model's license
terms when they download or deploy it.

